:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:55:32','2026-04-07 00:55:32','2026-04-07 00:55:32'),(32,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','96','telegram:7588358556','你在哪里',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:57:29','2026-04-07 00:57:30','2026-04-07 00:57:30'),(33,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','97',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:57:36','2026-04-07 00:57:36','2026-04-07 00:57:36'),(34,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','144','telegram:7588358556','OpenClaw 发过来的 outbound 记录 content 就是 null，说明 OpenClaw 的 chat-logger plugin 写入时没有把 agent 回复内容映射到 content\n   字段。                                                                                                                         \n                                                                                                                                  \n  这是 plugin 配置问题，需要在 OpenClaw 那边检查 chat-logger-plugin 的字段映射——outbound 消息的正文用的是什么字段名？看一下       \n  /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/chat-logger-plugin.tgz 里的配置',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:58:52','2026-04-07 00:58:52','2026-04-07 00:58:52'),(35,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','145',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:59:12','2026-04-07 00:59:12','2026-04-07 00:59:12'),(36,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','146',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:59:13','2026-04-07 00:59:13','2026-04-07 00:59:13'),(37,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','147',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 16:59:14','2026-04-07 00:59:14','2026-04-07 00:59:14'),(38,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','148','telegram:7588358556','重启了',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:00:08','2026-04-07 01:00:08','2026-04-07 01:00:08'),(39,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','149',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:00:45','2026-04-07 01:00:45','2026-04-07 01:00:45'),(40,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','150',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:00:47','2026-04-07 01:00:47','2026-04-07 01:00:47'),(41,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','151',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:00:48','2026-04-07 01:00:48','2026-04-07 01:00:48'),(42,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','152',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:00:49','2026-04-07 01:00:49','2026-04-07 01:00:49'),(43,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','153',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:00:50','2026-04-07 01:00:50','2026-04-07 01:00:50'),(44,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','154','telegram:7588358556','好了吗',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:01:12','2026-04-07 01:01:12','2026-04-07 01:01:12'),(45,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','155',NULL,'好了，看日志：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:01:39','2026-04-07 01:01:39','2026-04-07 01:01:39'),(46,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','156',NULL,'outbound 的字段是 `ctx.content`，内容完整有了！现在把 debug 日志去掉，handler 清理干净：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:01:40','2026-04-07 01:01:40','2026-04-07 01:01:40'),(47,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','157',NULL,'inbound 和 outbound 都用 `ctx.content`，完全一致。再把最新 handler 同步回源目录打包：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:01:41','2026-04-07 01:01:41','2026-04-07 01:01:41'),(48,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','158',NULL,'全部搞定 ✅ 重启一次让 debug 日志停掉：\n\n```bash\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n```',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:01:42','2026-04-07 01:01:42','2026-04-07 01:01:42'),(49,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','159','telegram:7588358556','测试一下',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:02:03','2026-04-07 01:02:03','2026-04-07 01:02:03'),(50,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','160',NULL,'已收到！等我回复后查数据库：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:02:31','2026-04-07 01:02:31','2026-04-07 01:02:31'),(51,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','161',NULL,'完美 ✅\n\n- `[inbound] agent=david | 测试一下` — 你的消息 ✅\n- `[outbound] agent=david | 全部搞定...` — 我的回复，内容完整 ✅\n\ninbound / outbound 内容都正确写入了，整套方案全部跑通！',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:02:32','2026-04-07 01:02:32','2026-04-07 01:02:32'),(52,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','100','telegram:7588358556','ni好',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:04:13','2026-04-07 01:04:13','2026-04-07 01:04:13'),(53,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','101',NULL,'🏪 你好David！我是舌尖门店AI助手，随时为您服务。\n\n现在是2026年4月7日早上9:04，湾仔店正在营业中。\n\n有什么需要我帮忙处理的吗？比如：\n- 查看当前库存情况\n- 补录销售情况（如\"XX商品卖完了\"）\n- 查看今日进货记录\n- 查看今日销售汇总\n- 录入新的进货信息\n- 或者其他门店管理操作',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:04:21','2026-04-07 01:04:21','2026-04-07 01:04:21'),(54,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','104','telegram:7588358556','在吗',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:13:22','2026-04-07 01:13:22','2026-04-07 01:13:22'),(55,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','106','telegram:7588358556','你在哪里',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:15:01','2026-04-07 01:15:01','2026-04-07 01:15:01'),(56,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','107',NULL,'🏪 我是舌尖门店AI助手，运行在云端服务器上，专门为您的湾仔店提供远程管理服务。\n\n我的主要功能包括：\n- 📦 库存管理（查询、补录、调整）\n- 💰 销售补录与查询\n- 🚛 进货管理\n- 📊 门店运营数据分析\n\n无论您在哪里，只要通过Telegram联系我，我就能帮您管理门店的日常运营工作。\n\n现在有什么需要我帮您处理的吗？',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:15:09','2026-04-07 01:15:09','2026-04-07 01:15:09'),(57,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','109','telegram:7588358556','？',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:02','2026-04-07 01:16:02','2026-04-07 01:16:02'),(58,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','110',NULL,'抱歉，我可能没理解您的意思。您是想问什么吗？\n\n我是舌尖门店AI助手，专门帮您管理湾仔店的运营工作。我可以帮您：\n\n1. 📦 **库存管理**：查库存、补录销售、调整库存\n2. 💰 **销售管理**：查看销售汇总、补录销售情况\n3. 🚛 **进货管理**：录入进货、查看进货记录\n4. 📊 **数据分析**：查看每日概览、操作日志\n\n您具体想了解什么或者需要什么帮助呢？',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:10','2026-04-07 01:16:10','2026-04-07 01:16:10'),(59,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','162','telegram:7588358556','重新打包',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:26','2026-04-07 01:16:27','2026-04-07 01:16:27'),(60,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','163',NULL,'打好了，路径：`/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-david/chat-logger-plugin.tgz`',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:39','2026-04-07 01:16:39','2026-04-07 01:16:39'),(61,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','164','telegram:7588358556','覆盖了吗',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:46','2026-04-07 01:16:46','2026-04-07 01:16:46'),(62,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','165',NULL,'覆盖了，刚才 `cp` 把最新的 handler.ts（已去掉 debug、content 字段已修正）同步到源目录再打包的，是最新版本。\n\n可以验证一下内容：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:57','2026-04-07 01:16:57','2026-04-07 01:16:57'),(63,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','166',NULL,'确认：\n- ✅ `content: ctx.content ?? null` — 正确字段\n- ✅ 无任何 debug 代码\n- ✅ API_URL 和 API_TOKEN 都在',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:16:58','2026-04-07 01:16:58','2026-04-07 01:16:58'),(64,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','167','telegram:7588358556','如果openclaw停止工作 不回复信息 如何设置重启呢',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:19:12','2026-04-07 01:19:12','2026-04-07 01:19:12'),(65,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','168',NULL,'Systemd 已经配了 `Restart=always`，进程崩溃会自动重启。但如果是卡死（进程还在但不响应），需要额外的看门狗机制。\n\n几个方案：\n\n---\n\n**方案1：加 watchdog cron（推荐）**\n\n每分钟检查一次，没响应就重启：\n\n```bash\ncrontab -e\n```\n\n加这行：\n```bash\n* * * * * /home/ubuntu/.npm-global/bin/openclaw gateway status 2>/dev/null | grep -q \"RPC probe: ok\" || systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n---\n\n**方案2：用 OpenClaw 自带的 healthcheck**\n\nOpenClaw 有内置 healthcheck 功能，可以定期自检。看看有没有相关配置：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:19:41','2026-04-07 01:19:41','2026-04-07 01:19:41'),(66,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','169',NULL,'OpenClaw 能检测 session stuck 但不会自动重启。**cron watchdog 是最实用的方案**，直接设置：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:19:42','2026-04-07 01:19:42','2026-04-07 01:19:42'),(67,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','170',NULL,'现在没有 crontab，帮你加上：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:19:43','2026-04-07 01:19:43','2026-04-07 01:19:43'),(68,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','171',NULL,'Gateway 掉了，需要你先重启：\n\n```bash\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n重启好之后我继续帮你配 watchdog cron。',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:19:44','2026-04-07 01:19:44','2026-04-07 01:19:44'),(69,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','172','telegram:7588358556','重启了',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:20:36','2026-04-07 01:20:36','2026-04-07 01:20:36'),(70,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','173',NULL,'Gateway 又掉了，看来不稳定。先在终端跑这几条命令：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 重启 gateway\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n\n# 2. 写 watchdog 脚本\ncat > /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh << \'EOF\'\n#!/bin/bash\nif ! /home/ubuntu/.npm-global/bin/openclaw gateway status 2>/dev/null | grep -q \"RPC probe: ok\"; then\n    echo \"[$(date)] restarting...\" >> /tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log\n    systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\nfi\nEOF\nchmod +x /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh\n\n# 3. 加 crontab（每分钟检查）\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"* * * * * /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh\") | crontab -\n\n# 4. 验证\ncrontab -l\n```\n\n四步一起跑完告诉我结果。',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:21:05','2026-04-07 01:21:05','2026-04-07 01:21:05'),(71,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','174','telegram:7588358556','你可以帮我跑吗',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:21:32','2026-04-07 01:21:32','2026-04-07 01:21:32'),(72,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','175',NULL,'可以，但需要你先批准，因为涉及写文件和修改 crontab：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:21:41','2026-04-07 01:21:41','2026-04-07 01:21:41'),(73,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','176',NULL,'Gateway 还是断开状态，审批通道也不通。需要你先在终端手动重启：\n\n```bash\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n重启好了之后我立刻帮你跑剩下的。',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:21:43','2026-04-07 01:21:43','2026-04-07 01:21:43'),(74,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','177','telegram:7588358556','重启了',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:22:04','2026-04-07 01:22:04','2026-04-07 01:22:04'),(75,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','178',NULL,'Gateway 刚重启完还没 pair 上，等几秒再试：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:22:36','2026-04-07 01:22:36','2026-04-07 01:22:36'),(76,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','179',NULL,'好了，现在跑：',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:22:38','2026-04-07 01:22:38','2026-04-07 01:22:38'),(77,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','180',NULL,'奇怪，RPC 刚才还是 ok 的。这个错误不是 gateway 的问题，是我这边的执行权限被 gateway pairing 拦住了。\n\n直接在你终端跑这三条：\n\n```bash\ncat > /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh << \'EOF\'\n#!/bin/bash\nif ! /home/ubuntu/.npm-global/bin/openclaw gateway status 2>/dev/null | grep -q \"RPC probe: ok\"; then\n    echo \"[$(date)] restarting...\" >> /tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log\n    systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\nfi\nEOF\n\nchmod +x /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh\n\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"* * * * * /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh\") | crontab -\n```\n\n完成后 `crontab -l` 看一下结果告诉我。',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:22:39','2026-04-07 01:22:39','2026-04-07 01:22:39'),(78,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','181','telegram:7588358556','* * * * * /home/ubuntu/.openclaw/watchdog.sh',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:23:06','2026-04-07 01:23:06','2026-04-07 01:23:06'),(79,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','182',NULL,'完美 ✅ \n\nwatchdog 已生效，每分钟自动检查一次。如果 gateway 不响应就自动重启，重启记录会写到 `/tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log`。\n\n以后可以用这个看重启历史：\n```bash\ncat /tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log\n```',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:23:13','2026-04-07 01:23:13','2026-04-07 01:23:13'),(80,'david','inbound','telegram','david2','telegram:7588358556','183','telegram:7588358556','好',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:23:33','2026-04-07 01:23:33','2026-04-07 01:23:33'),(81,'david','outbound','telegram','david2','7588358556','184',NULL,'今天搞定了不少东西，总结一下：\n\n**✅ 完成清单**\n- `chat-logger` plugin — 所有 agent 收发消息自动写入 Laravel MySQL\n- inbound / outbound 内容完整，agent_id 正确\n- watchdog cron — 每分钟检查，gateway 挂了自动重启\n- 打包好了 `chat-logger-plugin.tgz`，给新客户两条命令装好\n\n有其他问题随时找我。',1,NULL,'agent:david:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:23:41','2026-04-07 01:23:41','2026-04-07 01:23:41'),(82,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','111','telegram:7588358556','你好',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:25:28','2026-04-07 01:25:28','2026-04-07 01:25:28'),(83,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','112',NULL,'🏪 你好David！我是舌尖门店AI助手，随时为您服务。\n\n现在是2026年4月7日早上9:25，湾仔店正在营业中。\n\n有什么需要我帮忙处理的吗？比如：\n- 查看当前库存情况\n- 补录销售情况（如\"XX商品卖完了\"）\n- 查看今日进货记录\n- 查看今日销售汇总\n- 录入新的进货信息\n- 或者其他门店管理操作',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:25:37','2026-04-07 01:25:37','2026-04-07 01:25:37'),(84,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','113','telegram:7588358556','/help',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:slash:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:25:40','2026-04-07 01:25:40','2026-04-07 01:25:40'),(85,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','114',NULL,'ℹ️ Help\n\nSession\n  /new  |  /reset  |  /compact [instructions]  |  /stop\n\nOptions\n  /think <level>  |  /model <id>  |  /fast status|on|off  |  /verbose on|off\n\nStatus\n  /status  |  /tasks  |  /whoami  |  /context\n\nSkills\n  /skill <name> [input]\n\nMore: /commands for full list, /tools for available capabilities',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:slash:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:25:40','2026-04-07 01:25:40','2026-04-07 01:25:40'),(86,'deepseek','inbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','115','telegram:7588358556','/new',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:slash:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:25:42','2026-04-07 01:25:42','2026-04-07 01:25:42'),(87,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','telegram:7588358556','116',NULL,'✅ New session started · model: deepseek/deepseek-chat',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:direct:7588358556','2026-04-06 17:25:45','2026-04-07 01:25:45','2026-04-07 01:25:45'),(88,'deepseek','outbound','telegram','deepseek','7588358556','118',NULL,'🏪 嗨David！我是舌尖门店AI助手，刚刚上线。今天有什么需要我帮忙处理的吗？比如库存查询、销售补录，还是其他门店管理事务？',1,NULL,'agent:deepseek:telegram:slash:7588358556','2026-0